WSUS App for Splunk

This app is designed to use information from the WSUS Add-on for Splunk and provide several specific views using that data.

Installation

This app can be installed via Splunk's UI under the Managed App section of Splunk Enterprise.  It only needs to be installed on Search Heads.

Configuration

This app makes use of the fields and queries used in the WSUS Add-on for Splunk.  The add-on should be installed and configured before utiliting this add-on.
